kelvin matthew sampson ( born october 5 , 1955 ) is the head coach of the houston cougars in the ncaa.   he previously was a men 's college basketball coach at montana tech ( 1981–85 ) , washington state university ( 1987–94 ) , the university of oklahoma ( 1994–2006 ) and indiana university ( 2006–08 ) .

